    "Duplicate articles are removed after the initial search has been conducted.",
    "The digital object identifiers were used to remove duplicate records.The third stage involved reading the remaining articles and determining whether they contributed to answering the research question.",
    "To determine whether articles meet the inclusion criteria, the authors screened the titles and abstracts of articles.",
    "An article that meets the inclusion criteria is screened for eligibility for the review through full-text screening.",
    "Lastly, irrelevant studies were excluded from the systematic review list at the final stage."
